Definition: the quality of being meager
Example: an exiguity of cloth that would only allow of miniature capes-George Eliot
Synonyms: adj, all, meager, meagreness, meagre, leanness, insufficient, lean, unprofitable, poorness, poor, scantiness, scanty, scantness, scant, exiguity, exiguous, insufficiency, the, quality, of, being, an, cloth, that, would, only, allow, miniature, capes, -George, Eliot
Category: noun.attribute
